snippet.title: PlayStation - Click Manga - Ginga Eiyuu Densetsu 1 (1999)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Click Manga: Ginga Eiyuu Densetsu 1 is an Action game, published by Tokuma Shoten, which was released in Japan in 1999.
